2. Convert snake_case to kebab-case
3. Update curl examples

Changes:
- `/local-api/trades/:mint` → `/trades/:mint`
- `/local-api/labs/wallet_trades_snapshot` → `/labs/wallet-trades-snapshot`
- `/local-api/ext/registry` → `/ext/registry`
- etc.

Also update any curl command examples to use new routes.
  </action>
  <verify>grep '/local-api/' ENDPOINTS.md returns no matches</verify>
  <done>ENDPOINTS.md uses clean routes throughout</done>
